title: Seed Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Macrobiotic, Organic, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Quick service vegan cafe near the Venice Beach boardwalk. Offers a varied menu with paninis and burgers, bowls and salads, fries, and vegan baked goods such as cookies and scones (on the weekends). Beverages include green teas, organic coffee, fresh pressed juices. All food is served in biodegradable disposable ware.
